Lingua::RU::PhTranslit version 0.4
=================================

Phonetic correct translit recoder from/to koi8/windows-1251.

Translit is writing cyrillic(russian) symbols by ASCII symbols (0x20-0x7f).

Function is reverse (koi2phtr <=> phtr2koi)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

perl 5
no dependecies to gcc (this is raw perl module)

